at the end

1. *Iskreno* se nadam da ćeš uspeti. (I sincerely hope that you will succeed.)
2. Kada je reč o iskrenosti, ona je vrlo značajna. (When it comes to sincerity, it is very important.)
3. Imamo iskreni interes da dođe do pomirenja. (We have a sincere interest in reconciliation.)
4. Uvek ću biti iskren prema tebi. (I will always be honest with you.)
5. Njegovi iskreni izrazi bili su pravi lek za moju tugu. (His sincere expressions were a real cure for my sorrow.)
6. *Iskren* da budem, nisam zadovoljan njegovim odgovorom. (To be honest, I am not satisfied with his answer.)